'''William O'Connor''' was an illustrator. He worked with [[Chris Trevas]] to illustrate ''[[The New Essential Guide to Alien Species]]'', providing roughly half of the book's artworks. Concept artist and illustrator, he also worked on ''Magic:The Gathering'' and ''Dungeons and Dragons''.

